               <p>OLD COURT.</p>
               <p>SECOND DAY. FRIDAY, DECEMBER 5.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury - Before Mr. Sergeant Arabin.</p>
               <p>54. 
               
                  <persName id="t18281204-53-defend529" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     DEACON
                  <interp inst="t18281204-53-defend529" type="surname" value="DEACON"></interp>
